    "faqs": [
      {
        "question": "Is the contrast injection painful?",
        "answer": "Most patients feel only a cool sensation; discomfort is minimal.\n"
      },
      {
        "question": "How soon will I get my neck MRI results?",
        "answer": "Standard reports are online the same evening for scans before 2 pm; next morning for later slots.\n"
      },
      {
        "question": "Can I drive after the scan?",
        "answer": "Yes, unless you received sedation—then arrange a companion.\n"
      },
      {
        "question": "What if I’m allergic to shellfish?",
        "answer": "Shellfish allergy does NOT predict gadolinium allergy. Tell the team anyway; pre-medication is possible.\n"
      },
      {
        "question": "Does insurance cover MRI neck with contrast?",
        "answer": "Most comprehensive policies reimburse 80–100 %. Our front desk helps with pre-authorization.\n"
      }
